name: 420GlitchAlien #3
description:
The #420GlitchAlien Series are an original @kayvonleenft abstract gif collectibles. 

With the future of NFT fractionalisation & collectors in mind this series will be 1:1 collectables & editions. 

These will be soft launched and will not be advertised on any social media & other variants in the series will be minted across other platforms to offer people across blockchain networks the same opportunity to find these limited edition gems!
